title: A video story about "The greatest number you can represent with three cylinders " is not known
subtitle: A viral story that claims that Ed Tres has received a standardized math test that has changed throughout the country full of questionable aspects.
author: Dan Evon
vclaim: Ed Trace managed to press for all the standard math tests in the country after his daughter answered "right" to the question, "What's the biggest number you can do with three numbers?" He was a wrong teacher.
